ADsafe uses JSLint to do its static analysis of widgets and library modules.
adsafe.js is the runtime component.



adsafe.js is the Ajax library that provides the widget with limit DOM access.

template.html is a template for an ADsafe widget.

template.js is a template for an ADsafe library module.



index.html describes ADsafe.

dom.html describes ADsafe's DOM interface.

widget.html describes the structure of ADsafe widgets.

adsafe.gif is the ADsafe logo.
